OL,2,MProject CETI: How to Decode the
OL,4,MLanguage of Other Species
OL,6,CSarah de Haas
OL,7,CFri 16:40-17:10
OL,8,CStage B
OL,10,GProject CETI is an interdisciplinary
OL,11,Gresearch project that uses new
OL,12,Gtechniques in data collection,
OL,13,Ganalysis, and artificial intelligence
OL,14,Gto understand what sperm whales are
OL,15,Gsaying to each other. The project
OL,16,Gincludes researchers from multiple
OL,17,Guniversities and institutions around
OL,18,Gthe world, spanning disciplines across
OL,19,Gmarine biology, robotics,
OL,20,Gcryptography, artificial intelligence,
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
